-- Turkish Soldier Dies in Roadside Bomb Attack, Hurriyet Reports
-- B y   E m r e   P e k e r
-- 2012-04-10T07:16:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-10/turkish-soldier-dies-in-roadside-bomb-attack-hurriyet-reports.html
A Turkish soldier died in a
roadside bomb attack in the northern province of Amasya,
Hurriyet  reported .  Six soldiers were wounded in the blast that occurred
yesterday as a military vehicle was returning to base following
a theft investigation, according to the Istanbul-based
newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emre Peker in Ankara at 
 epeker2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
